              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "FIPA-ACL introduced performatives (REQUEST, INFORM, PROPOSE, FAILURE) that remain the conceptual foundation of modern protocols like A2A and ACP."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
